                    <p>PayPal stands as a renowned digital payment platform, allowing individuals and businesses to send and receive money globally. However, its utility in Nigeria remains somewhat limited. While it offers convenience and ease of use, Nigerian users often encounter restrictions, such as limitations on receiving payments directly into their Nigerian accounts.</p>
